00:07:52.920 --> 00:07:53.760
Wen Yun.

00:07:54.360 --> 00:07:55.510
Wen Yun, you can't sleep.

00:07:56.310 --> 00:07:57.160
You must stay awake.

00:07:57.720 --> 00:07:58.560
Hang in there.

00:08:00.120 --> 00:08:03.120
