00:20:32.590 --> 00:20:33.430
Tell me.

00:20:33.680 --> 00:20:35.110
I will get them

00:20:35.270 --> 00:20:36.200
at whatever cost.

00:20:39.350 --> 00:20:40.550
It takes a lot of effort

00:20:40.920 --> 00:20:42.160
