00:20:42.790 --> 00:20:43.960
It takes a lot of strength.

00:20:44.310 --> 00:20:45.750
Two hours is needed for a day.

00:20:45.920 --> 00:20:46.760
And it must be done

00:20:47.000 --> 00:20:48.160
